                    div(class="row mb30 ta-c mt30 showTo-md")
                        img(src="unit_1/module_4/assets/images/act_6_1.png", alt="" class="u-responsive-img w80")
                    button(class="c-btn-Icon u-bgIconListen mt20" ng-audio="unit_1/module_4/assets/audios/act_6_1.mp3")
                        span Conversación 1
                    div(class="row mt20")
                        div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                | What are you doing on Friday?
                        div(class="mb20 row-flex mt20")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  B. 
                                | I am going #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")] on Friday afternoon.
                    button(class="c-btn-Icon u-bgIconListen mt20" ng-audio="unit_1/module_4/assets/audios/act_6_2.mp3")
                        span Conversación 2
                    div(class="row mt20")
                        div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                | Sir, can I help you with anything else?
                        div(class="mb20 row-flex mt20")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  B. 
                                | Please, can you #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")] for me in that nice Italian restaurant?
                        div(class="col-flex")
                                strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                | Sure.
                div(class="col-flex-xs12 col-flex-md6 col-center mt10-sm mt10-md")
                        button(class="c-btn-Icon u-bgIconListen mt20" ng-audio="unit_1/module_4/assets/audios/act_6_3.mp3")
                            span Conversación 3
                        div(class="row mt20")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                    | Will you #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")]? Help me carry this table.
                            div(class="mb20 row-flex mt20")
                                div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  B. 
                                    | Sure. Where do you want us to put it?
                        button(class="c-btn-Icon u-bgIconListen mt20" ng-audio="unit_1/module_4/assets/audios/act_6_4.mp3")
                            span Conversación 4
                        div(class="row mt20")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                    | Thanks, Doctor. When should I come again?
                            div(class="mb20 row-flex mt20")
                                div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  B. 
                                    | Let’s #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")] for 10:00 in the morning next Tuesday. Does that work for you?
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                    | Yes, perfect.
                        button(class="c-btn-Icon u-bgIconListen mt20" ng-audio="unit_1/module_4/assets/audios/act_6_5.mp3")
                            span Conversación 5
                        div(class="row mt20")
                            div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  A. 
                                    | Oh, dear! There is so much #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")]!
                            div(class="mb20 row-flex mt20")
                                div(class="col-flex")
                                    strong(class="u-textColor_4-dark")  B. 
                                    | Don’t worry. I’ll help you.

